<collectingRegion box="[825,912,1328,1354]" country="Mexico" name="Mexico" pageId="12" pageNumber="237">Mexico</collectingRegion>
, and the State of 
<collectingRegion box="[140,242,1364,1390]" country="Mexico" name="Durango" pageId="12" pageNumber="237">Durango</collectingRegion>
in northern 
<collectingCountry box="[387,474,1363,1389]" name="Mexico" pageId="12" pageNumber="237">Mexico</collectingCountry>
. Collecting dates range from mid-July to mid-August.
</paragraph>
